  <brief_title>The Effect of Oral Polymeric Diet Enriched With TGF-beta 2 (Modulen) on Clinical Response and Mucosal Healing in Adult Patients With Newly Diagnosed Crohn's Disease</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effect of Oral Polymeric Diet Enriched With TGF-beta 2 (Modulen) on Clinical Response and Mucosal Healing in Adult Patients With Newly Diagnosed Crohn's Disease: a Prospective, Randomized Study</official_title>
  <sponsors>
